snippet.textDisplay: During 2017 Nh7 Weekender Pune, Mame Khan performed with his band. Few people had heard of him otherwise - people had come for cigarettes after sex etc. His performance was so engaging and energetic that people from other parallel events came to his stage. People were dancing with crazy energy and patently indian dance moves, the kind you wouldn't see at EDM concerts. It was truly one of the best concert experiences I've had!
